{"tid":511566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到完場］一人一信反對縮短選舉投票時間 諮詢期今日（29日）完結！","createTime":"2017-12-27T15:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T15:34:39.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ba07ed0ea21c839d906de0947ebaefbbed0f24","tid":511566,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"【最後機會！一人一信反對縮短投票時間】<br />\n政府正諮詢縮短日後選舉投票時間的建議，諮詢期12月29日結束！2016年立法會選舉最後一個小時投票人數近22萬，是投票高峰。縮短投票時間除不便需要上班的市民，亦是剝奪市民的選舉權！請即簽署，向政制及內地事務局發聲，反對縮短日後選舉投票時間的建議！只需一分鐘，你的意見將直接發送至政府電郵！請大家大力SHARE！<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"http://p.charlesmok.hk/keepvotetime\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp.charlesmok.hk%2Fkeepvotetime&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=03c02b87\" target=\"_blank\">p.charlesmok.hk/keepvotetime</a><br />\n諮詢文件：<a href=\"http://www.cmab.gov.hk/doc/issues/Consultation_Paper-Electoral_Arrangements_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmab.gov.hk%2Fdoc%2Fissues%2FConsultation_Paper-Electoral_Arrangements_c.pdf&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=a0492aa6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cmab.gov.hk/doc/issues/Consultation_Paper-Electoral_Arrangements_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/posts/1628481440552510:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCharlesMokOffice%2Fposts%2F1628481440552510%3A0&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=869ee60d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CharlesMokOffice/posts/1628481440552510:0</a><br />\n<br />\n...市民可在下月29日或之前將意見郵寄至添馬添美道2號政府總部東翼12樓政制及內地事務局、傳真至2840 1976，或以電郵提交。(rea_consultation@cmab.gov.hk)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.news.gov.hi/tc/categories/admin/html/2017/11/20171113_164552.lin.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hi%2Ftc%2Fcategories%2Fadmin%2Fhtml%2F2017%2F11%2F20171113_164552.lin.shtml&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=0286cae9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.news.gov.hi/tc/categories/admin/html/2017/11/20171113_164552.lin.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然未必有用但希望各位略盡綿力<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7320a81e2af0f41c667d0c4b6898aa754ec2f59d","tid":511566,"uid":116530,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/233116_9ab1e616f3c2ac0d41a1e036733cbfc3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F233116_9ab1e616f3c2ac0d41a1e036733cbfc3.jpeg&h=116cce63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8849b9da158150a0810eab8219d0ca8d249d3ba8","tid":511566,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7320a81e2af0f41c667d0c4b6898aa754ec2f59d","tid":511566,"uid":116530,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/233116_9ab1e616f3c2ac0d41a1e036733cbfc3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F233116_9ab1e616f3c2ac0d41a1e036733cbfc3.jpeg&h=116cce63&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}